
This repo have some ansible automation use cases
1. user creation and delection
2. enable/Disable usb from windows machines
3. Setup banner on Windows machine
4. Lock user if 3 wrong attempt
5. Setup a NTP server on rhel
6. Sync Windows machne with rhel time server
7. Send a Notification using mail about host,username,random_password to pre_configured user
8. check ssl of site and send mail Notification
9. Linux Server patching and Basic Reporting.
10. EDA windows basic ping to test if server is reachable 

EDA sample command
curl -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d "{\"deviceId\" : \"id representing a device uniquely in SmartHub INFER\",\"deviceName\": \"Friendly name of the device in SmartHub INFER\",\"orgName\": \"Org name in SmartHub INFER\",\"deviceIp\" : \"Leena-Win\", \"action\" : \"disallow usb storage\" }" 127.0.0.1:5000/endpoint
curl -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d "{\"deviceId\" : \"id representing a device uniquely in SmartHub INFER\",\"deviceName\": \"Friendly name of the device in SmartHub INFER\",\"orgName\": \"Org name in SmartHub INFER\",\"deviceIp\" : \"Leena-Win\", \"action\" : \"allow usb storage\" }" 127.0.0.1:5000/endpoint
curl -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d "{\"deviceId\" : \"id representing a device uniquely in SmartHub INFER\",\"deviceName\": \"Friendly name of the device in SmartHub INFER\",\"orgName\": \"Org name in SmartHub INFER\",\"deviceIp\" : \"Leena-Win\", \"action\" : \"Rotate password\" }" 127.0.0.1:5000/endpoint
